ZH: 零售业是一个重要的经济领域。
EN: The retail industry is an important economic sector.

ZH: 大型商场是我国零售业的代表。
EN: Large shopping malls represent the retail industry in our country.

ZH: 我在一家大型零售连锁店工作。
EN: I work at a large retail chain store.

ZH: 随着互联网的发展，电子商务带动了零售业的繁荣。
EN: With the development of the internet, e-commerce has driven the prosperity of the retail industry.

ZH: 零售店提供各种各样的商品。
EN: Retail stores offer a wide variety of products.

ZH: 这家零售店实行了降价促销。
EN: This retail store has implemented price reductions and promotions.

ZH: 零售商需要维持良好的客户关系。
EN: Retailers need to maintain good customer relationships.

ZH: 我们需要提供更好的零售体验，以吸引更多的顾客。
EN: We need to provide a better retail experience to attract more customers.

ZH: 零售业的竞争非常激烈。
EN: The competition in the retail industry is very fierce.

ZH: 这次活动是为了促进零售业的发展。
EN: This event is aimed at promoting the development of the retail industry.

ZH: 零售领域的创新可以带来巨大的商机。
EN: Innovations in the retail sector can bring tremendous business opportunities.

ZH: 零售店员需要具备良好的销售技巧。
EN: Retail clerks need to have good sales skills.

ZH: 这家零售商在全国各地都有分店。
EN: This retailer has branches all over the country.

ZH: 零售业对物流的要求非常高。
EN: The retail industry has high requirements for logistics.

ZH: 这个村庄的经济主要依靠农产品的零售。
EN: The economy of this village mainly relies on the retail of agricultural products.

ZH: 随着消费者需求的变化，零售业在不断调整经营策略。
EN: With the changing consumer demand, the retail industry is constantly adjusting its business strategies.

ZH: 这家零售店开设了一条专门的退换货窗口。
EN: This retail store has opened a dedicated return and exchange counter.

ZH: 在节假日期间，零售店经常会举办促销活动。
EN: Retail stores often hold promotions during holidays and festivals.

ZH: 这个品牌在零售业占有重要地位。
EN: This brand occupies an important position in the retail industry.

ZH: 零售业发展迅速，为社会创造了大量就业机会。
EN: The rapid development of the retail industry has created numerous job opportunities for society.
